{
  "stem": "14613.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And one more thing-- which I had the privilege, while I worked there, that my brother and myself, we could finish the production really very fast, and then, because of the circumstances that we knew the people, the supervisor and the director, we were able maybe somehow, illegally, to sneak out from the resort, go to the field, and cultivate vegetables in the garden, and so on, that gave us also a great benefit.",
      "word_count": 74
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My-- my brother worked part of the time with me, and my sister also worked, sometimes in different places.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My older sister worked, and the younger-- I mean, they were both older than me-- but the older sister worked also in the resort places.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My younger sister-- they both worked-- part of the time they had better job, because part of the time they worked in a bakery-- in a bakery, where they made bread.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was a very good position, because at least you could get some extra food while you were at work.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You were not supposed to smuggle out anything, but while they worked, they were able to get more bread.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So that helped quite a bit, because then they didn't have eat so much at home.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my mother worked, also.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Everyone had to work.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And my mother worked, also, in a resort-- in a sewing resort.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And my father worked there, too.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "As I said, he didn't want to take a leadership role.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And and he died in ghetto, early-- of course, he died really, we can call it, from malnutrition, and so on, because he had some ulcers, and it was the improper diet which he had in ghetto, it just flared up a few times.",
      "word_count": 44
    }
  ],
